Case No. 12-cv-701-EGS

STIPULATION OF SETTLEMENT AND DISMISSAL

Plaintiff Frederick Simms, and defendants, the District of Columbia, Cathy Lanier, and

Vincent Gray, have agreed to a settlement in this case. The parties agree to dismiss this action

with prejudice, and each party will bear its own costs and attorneys’ fees.

